{"tid":2371,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［LIHKG］策略研討會","createTime":"2016-11-25T19:38:15.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-26T13:09:29.000Z","uid":14583,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2cdb7d1d70e7aefb12535b691cc0ba17098c0a0a","tid":2371,"uid":14583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T19:38:15.000Z","msg":"高登係一個討論區，但係對各位巴打絲打黎講，更加係一個idea，一個人人希望自由言論既地方。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n無論係an 狗、ifandog、本民狗、青狗、熱狗、獌狗、車狗、痢狗、阿狗，每條狗，點互咬都好，都需要一個好既地方比佢能夠講佢所想。<br />\n<br />\n眼見高登日益腐敗，言論自由更加被打壓，高登仔狗咬狗骨都係等閒事。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而家LIHKG 既出現，好有可能從此將高登界開兩半。<span style=\"color: red;\">而人聲單薄既高登仔，只係一群污合之眾，日後網上規管一旦實施，要滅聲相信唔係難事。</span> 所以當務之急就係團結力量。<br />\n<br />\n有見及此，小弟希望借今次LIHKG 呢次小風波，集合眾巴打既合力，一齊幫香港網絡討論鳳凰涅槃，浴火重生。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以下係小弟拋磚引玉既諗法，純粹亂up , 非常支持各位巴打出謀獻策。由於此post 純作研討用，請注意以下幾點<br />\n1. 請自重避免流於表面既口角之爭<br />\n2. 如有任何實際行動，請另外開post<br />\n3. 請謹記此post 之目的為協助LIHKG 擴展成一個真正容許言論自由既地方，而且比以往高登更具影響力<br />\n<br />\n入正題，是咁的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n䇿略一 - 成功完美吸納舊高登及膠登之人流<br />\n1. 小弟認為人一定有惰性，除非有一個非做不可既理由，否則好難突然改變人既行為模式。因為咁，所以係 android launch 呢段時間， 要充分証明到無論係post 既質量度同人流量， LIHKG 都遠勝高登<br />\n<br />\n2. 招納活躍用戶，需知高登咁吸引，除左言論自由之外，經典膠POST 絕對重要，因此，要成功呼喚所有小圈子同活躍USER 用LIHKG<br />\n<br />\n策略二 - LIHKG 持續改善<br />\n1. 要知道高登十年如一日慢，十年如一日既界面，係十年前或者仲得，但黎到而家呢個年代。user experience 更為重要，因此小弟希望呢個post 亦可以匯合各類意見比連住尼巴打發展用<br />\n<br />\n暫時brainstorm 左咁多，餘下就靠各位巴打絲打了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08041c268711305a91b855ba825c68e035783e16","tid":2371,"uid":14583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T19:39:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db2d260fac89cf0e9c1efa83be2fd18dd128ebba","tid":2371,"uid":14583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T19:40:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"394004f7b828af9ba0ec33b231e743443b6be10e","tid":2371,"uid":14583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T19:41:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff9ccd3983e213385329ac09353e847ad6a3d04c","tid":2371,"uid":14583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T19:42:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢個鐘數是咪太夜"},{"pid":"e6c7214de4bd0b9668f7a14e889e0626dbe10a79","tid":2371,"uid":11349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T19:44:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />