d":2371,"uid":16418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T19:49:24.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實依家最擔心係新屎坑三日香，同埋android機啲巴打唔轉會<br />\nLINKG嘅developer一定要爭氣！先穩定咗個server先 再完善埋個app啲功能，例如揀台排序嗰啲..."},{"pid":"b72472a98b0fd274b74fc78108d668e92b1853cc","tid":2371,"uid":14583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T19:50:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>禁止簡體字同5p字有無可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實換個角度諗，利用林早洩filter 既idea, 將簡體字同 5p 字都filter 變正常字，咁久而久之就冇人再用簡體字同5p字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n當然可能涉及自由問題，但係應該可以用其他方法解決"},{"pid":"a80ef7807d78e8ce96eb7eb9a40c82bce47a8416","tid":2371,"uid":11721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T19:51:24.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3af10098924cd2a539b2caa5538b9f4d90b4346e","tid":2371,"uid":14583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T19:53:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實依家最擔心係新屎坑三日香，同埋android機啲巴打唔轉會<br />\nLINKG嘅developer一定要爭氣！先穩定咗個server先 再完善埋個app啲功能，例如揀台排序嗰啲...</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nIOS 用戶應該可以煲翻三五七日，但係說Android機轉會係好難，暫時諗到最可能就係當高登水靜河飛既時候，佢地要搵j 圖 搵故搵笑料都要黎呢到，咁就可以由唔可能變可能"},{"pid":"495482a9eced7af9f105a7664d12465d329ac8f7","tid":2371,"uid":14583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T19:53:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔該巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe58f03908aee04324bb67746d825b7f8